➜湖北诗人朱翠荣（清美玉洁）：原创《祝贺出窑的青花瓷》
http://www.sohu.com/a/424860845_100115135	30761
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201015/b4da7e808a824c88953985ebf4fe35ad.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>原创《祝贺出窑的青花瓷》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/朱翠荣（武汉）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">打磨青天白日，有地通天</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">都在一声令下，布施的观音</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有勤劳的双手掏出陶土，磊砌瓷窑</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">祝贺一场大典</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">宛如一场恋爱进入婚姻的角色</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">血与灵肉的交织，思想唤醒的火花</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">撒播美的种子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">受孕率不高不低</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">孕育的过程不长也不短</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">坯胎造型各异，大小长短不一</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在大子宫里拿捏得精心，郑重公正摆放</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">点燃炉火，守到分娩</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">纯青的境界里跳动着火焰光星</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">青花瓷亮丽古今</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">更惊亮默默等候彩釉出炉的我们</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">恭恭敬敬地欣赏细观</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
