➜江西诗人时差先生：路上
http://www.sohu.com/a/424862554_100115135	31211
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201015/09738f6e1dcc40cc887c242f61639583.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>路上</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/时差先生</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">脚踩在那戈壁泥土</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一阵风</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">卷起亿万年的咸味</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">尘埃向人们解释</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这是它死去之后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">唯一有人发现它</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最有价值的告白</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">该条路期待修理</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大抵是缺乏水的柔性</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">泥土与砂石很难走到交集</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">翻斗车拉来的粘泥</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">与戈壁石自由组合</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">交变着一场电闪雷鸣的舞</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">压路机含着多年的烟斗</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">想起了它的情人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">时光穿过一个个日子</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
